{"tid":451594,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 香煎豬扒併炒蘑菇","createTime":"2017-10-29T11:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T00:00:24.000Z","uid":74981,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bea90378b8adc54cec5126d9ccebc9e71b440974","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/29j30tszi7/20171029_181320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F29j30tszi7%2F20171029_181320.jpg&h=517b7ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PiPWe4PCOS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPiPWe4PCOS0&d=NpjW283%2FYonYtd0K1zRA5sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3d7ac42d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PiPWe4PCOS0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n普通豬扒1塊<br />\n蘑菇8粒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>調味:</ins></strong><br />\n蒜蓉2茶匙<br />\n黑胡椒1茶匙<br />\n鹽半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>醃料A:</ins></strong><br />\n白米醋1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>醃料B:</ins></strong><br />\n生抽2茶匙<br />\n糖1/3茶匙<br />\n酒1茶匙<br />\n生粉水少許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法: (蘑菇)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 蘑菇洗乾淨抹乾<br />\n<br />\n2. 獲落油燒至微熱, 落蒜蓉炒香, 落埋蘑菇, 黑椒炒.<br />\n<br />\n3. 贊水炒, 以蒸氣同水溫令佢快D熟, 收水時乾左未熟, 再贊水炒, 重覆贊水步驟至蘑菇收縮全熟, 拎走備用. <br />\n<br />\n4. 蘑菇原粒炒唔切片, 確保口感同JUICY效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法: (豬扒)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 豬扒解凍, 以醃料A醃15-20分鐘, 然後用水洗走醃料A, 抹乾.<br />\n<br />\n2. 以醃料B醃10分鐘.<br />\n<br />\n3. 熱獲落油, 大火煎封2邊, 轉小火將兩邊煎熟, 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006858f3b05fc237d5aa11e6b96ed65dcc49c57b","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"唔記得講, 如用梅頭豬扒, 請省卻用醋醃步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d19254d3ebc68359d042e70c3953cee4be9a40d","tid":451594,"uid":114064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"狗狗煮飯比我食得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026ea859de07d905666705461fbbe7fcbb8276a9","tid":451594,"uid":13541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e392c221c38ec9ada3ae7842d5b831e4848fba67","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗狗煮飯比我食得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49334e087466913b98f4cc47fd9ef66624df4fd","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45636000df19eb4ef20325ca8821e698c3575b30","tid":451594,"uid":56401,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥絲咪同你天生一對"},{"pid":"4ee797cf89deb7b792541227d3df7c78c84f4d77","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥絲咪同你天生一對</blockquote><br />\n佢只係本癲狗隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d770fdc20c95cd1b64b2a38ff6fbe51f19a9b57","tid":451594,"uid":86037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥絲咪同你天生一對</blockquote><br />\n佢只係本癲狗隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b13d4f5412d1b4ca8c1ad3afe1ec82d30db4309","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>結婚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥絲咪同你天生一對</blockquote><br />\n佢只係本癲狗隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c8a5ce769bfdd781a8284bb00a22f6ca74a560","tid":451594,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔記得講, 如用梅頭豬扒, 請省卻用醋醃步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<br />\n超市d扒要唔要醋，有咩用"},{"pid":"151b562a588d669764f10ce7bca47d432cbaf533","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔記得講, 如用梅頭豬扒, 請省卻用醋醃步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<br />\n超市d扒要唔要醋，有咩用</blockquote><br />\n醋主要係代替鬆肉粉將d嚡位那鬆，如果係梅頭豬扒就冇咩嚡位，可以唔洗用醋那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過，唔好expect醋既效果會同鬆肉粉一樣勁，因為鬆肉粉係化學野食得多冇益所以我用醋代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48cc478b134a51a2b784f9d059f7abfb20932f2","tid":451594,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5730932ec9e57d56eae511c9511e230f407f1075","tid":451594,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9737a06183602a0ac8bc35a8ea486c5afe1adbd0","tid":451594,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de853a660f3dec5abd8f0f06b59add975011105f","tid":451594,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b5c12a8724b5a419aa133280d19153023b18bfb","tid":451594,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317a102f3b541d765b773fd6e8a44a03c9b0fc86","tid":451594,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fc3f1fc94bae4bc312be575797c0